commit.message: Version 1.10.2.
Guix: Message about database at the right place.
Guix: Format lists and empty properties properly in helm-system-packages-guix-info.
Guix: Clean up messages.
Guix: Re-enable TRAMP support.
Guix: Fix newline escaping in descriptions.
Guix: Add database support to all actions.
guix: Remove obsolete cache code.
guix: Generate database from Guix REPL for huge performance boost.

README: Update Voidlinux URL

The old link is dead and the website doesn't seem to be affiliated with Voidlinux anymore
Reorder package managers to fix `dpkg` being detected on fedora
Fix some doc typos
pacman: Fix wrong variable name in the documentation
pacman: Fix erroneous face name
removes quote desc-list on push
Guix: Add support for multiple channels

Really discard errors in -run and -call

This fixes some Guix actions like (reverse) dependency listings.
guix: Update cache whenever guix pull commit is different
guix: Fix -guix-refresh call in eshell-post-command-hook
readme: Warn about interface changes
dnf: add more actions

Fix helm min version requirement

helm-system-package uses :persistent-action-if which has been
introduced in helm 2.8.7.
dnf: add support for showing package information
